ller/nodeipam/ipam/cidr_allocator.go and pkg/controller/nodeipam/ipam/range_allocator.go for CIDR range management.\n\nNetwork plugin coordination is defined by the Runtime interface in pkg/kubelet/container/runtime.go, which specifies methods for UpdatePodCIDR and other network-related operations. The sync result tracking in pkg/kubelet/container/sync_result.go includes SetupNetwork action to track network setup failures.\n\nAdditional network configuration is handled in pkg/kubelet/kubelet_pods.go for pod-specific network settings, and pkg/kubelet/kubelet_network_linux.go manages Linux-specific network utilities like iptables firewall rules."
